程序包 data

类 Submission

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.Submission
  • public class Submission
extends java.lang.Object
    The Submission class models a submission that a student makes to the teacher. A submission will contain the names of the submission as well as the content inside. This class is immutable.
    作者:
    Kaz Nakao

      • Submission

        public Submission​(java.lang.String name,
                  java.lang.String content,
                  java.lang.String grade,
                  int rubric)
        For initializing a submission with a grade already set
        参数:
        name - Title of the submission
        content - The "content" of the submission. Essay material
        grade - The grade of the submission
        rubric - The index of the rubric in the classroom that this submission will be found in.

      • Submission

        public Submission​(java.lang.String name,
                  java.lang.String content,
                  int rubric)
        Creates a new submission object.
        参数:
        name - Name of the submission
        content - The essay material that is in the submission
        rubric - The index of the rubric in the classroom that this submission will be found in.
